body_html:
Hi Tatiana,
I am sorry for miss-reading your original comments. It was about pylint instead of cpplint.
My PR does not touch any python code so it should not cause any pylint error.

Future investigation shows that the "pylint" issue has been fixed by "yongtang" in last 24 hours.
You can check the history of this file: tensorflow/contrib/cmake/tools/create_def_file.py.

Regards,
GZ
